
Topics:

  CSS Transition/Animation

  Transition: props duration timing-function; height 1000ms ease-in-out;
  animation: name duration timing-function delay iteration-count direction fill-mode;
    eg: animation: sample-animation 2s ease-in infinite alternate;
      sample-animation ---> keyframes definition

